3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper employs deep networks to learn age-related patterns.
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper involves compiling evaluation datasets from different sources and performing detailed evaluations of the approach.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with age estimation of buildings from photographs, which can be considered as a multimedia task.
